attributes.additional_details:
Across the whole country there is a HUGE problem with the lack of nhs capacity in dentists!
All dentists now are either private only, which people just can not afford or they are not taking on NHS patients. People can't afford to have to pay a monthly fee of £10/20 then pay for any treatment in top. Nearly £50 for just a check up (£24 with NHS). This is unacceptable. People are suffering with bad oral problems, resorting to them taking drastic measures! 
Help us look after our teeth!
attributes.background:
***NHS DENTISTS CAPACITY***
Make more NHS availability to the public.

rejection.details: You may wish to sign this petition which calls for the same action: https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/625518
